visual_description.name: outdoor_event_dining_area.jpg
visual_description.description: White tables and chairs under a canopy, set on brick patio. Neutral palette, overcast daylight, minimal decoration, visible barn structure. Lighting flat, lacks color vibrancy, some cluttered arrangements.
visual_description.score_basis: Neutral, serene setup, but lacks strong visual impact. Overcast lighting makes scene flat, white color dominates, minimal decoration reduces warmth. Good clarity but no focal point. Suitable for casual event documentation.
